assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Wethaq Takaful Insurance Company K.S.C.P. engages in takaful insurance, investment, and car rental businesses in Kuwait. The company offers motor vehicle insurance products, including comprehensive, geographical extension, driving license, private personal accidents/orange card/road assistance/replacement vehicle, warranties, and TPL- all-terrain vehicle insurance; and fire and property insurance products comprising fire and allied perils/property all risk, house holders comprehensive, burglary, and plate glass insurance. It also provides construction and engineering insurance products, such as contractors all risks/rigs, erection all-risks, construction plant and machinery, machinery breakdown, electronic equipment, and workmen compensation insurance; and liability insurance products that consist of general third-party liability, employer's liability, hauliers, TPL-motor, and TPL-boat policies. In addition, the company offers group takaful and group medical insurance products comprising group takaful, group medical, workmen compensation, and personal accidents/domestic helpers, as well as travel assistance, such as schengen cover policies; financial insurance products for professional indemnity/medical malpractice, credit life, bankers blanket bond/investment management insurance/purchase protection and secure wallet programs/computer crimes/directors and officers, business interruptions, money in transit, and fidelity guarantee/money in safe; and marine and aviation insurance products for marine cargo, hull, aircrafts, and helicopters. Further, it is involved in purchase, sale, and lease of lands; real estate investment and marketing activities; and trading of cars and spare parts. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Kuwait City, Kuwait. Wethaq Takaful Insurance Company K.S.C.P. operates as a subsidiary of Investment Dar Company K.S.C.C.
